She stopped and looked at Lobstruck.
"Not good." She ducked when he fired on her, but she was hit by the 
optic blast. "AHHH!"  she limped over to the side of a tree and dove 
behind it.  She held her gun up and fired at Lobstruck from her cover.
"LEAVE ME ALONE!" she yelled while firing at him.
